deleteFile(uint256).details: Delete a file (only the owner can delete)

params._fileId: The ID of the file to delete

returns._0: True if the file exists, false otherwise

getFiles(uint256[]).details: Get file information for multiple files

returns._0: totalFiles The total number of files stored
returns._1: nextFileId The next available file ID

getUserFileCount(address).details: Get the total number of files uploaded by a user

returns._0: Number of files uploaded by the user

getUserFiles(address).details: Get all files uploaded by a specific user

returns._0: Array of file IDs belonging to the user

uploadFile(string,string,uint256).details: Upload a file's metadata to the blockchain

params._fileSize: The size of the file in bytes
params._ipfsHash: The IPFS hash of the uploaded file
